</title>
<subSubSection id="2820E402033B3EFA5BCF721718E3B29E" pageId="null" pageNumber="815" type="description">
<paragraph id="65CB5C5C9E47D92E7F6EEB651CAA8291" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">
Lockere Rasen bildend, mit wenigen sterilen Trieben. 
<normalizedToken id="BA7282592EF2399E7320287151E2C3FC" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
meist unterhalb der Mitte am breitesten, spitz, 1-2,5 cm lang. Haare an den 
<normalizedToken id="79A23883704736DD7CF8BBE071F1500A" originalValue="Blättern" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Blaettern</normalizedToken>
und am Kelch 0,3-0,5 mm lang. 
<emphasis id="5885A7A1E2D39B8C80D226010F074C24" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">
Oberste 
<normalizedToken id="D9ABF312AE45E4DD1D46AB64FED83BC0" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
im Blutenstand
</emphasis>
(nur an 
<normalizedToken id="BD7D6DBC62169604D4A2F5D2A4F9C49C" originalValue="mehrblütigen" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">mehrbluetigen</normalizedToken>
Exemplaren erkennbar) 
<emphasis id="8DD516BAEABF21A114E356DA0FF80376" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">
klein, auf der Oberseite 
<normalizedToken id="FE552717862CD63D89076993658D3F90" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">+/-</normalizedToken>
kahl, mit 
<normalizedToken id="A67384535F73EF525D383F308B7F838F" originalValue="trockenhäutiger" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">trockenhaeutiger</normalizedToken>
Spitze.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="8D58FD7CBEFAE89E06A53887540E2293" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="1B0D53066990759EAF002CBEB609788A" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">+/-</normalizedToken>
stumpf. 
<normalizedToken id="458B2BCCDE310B719B03839EC1DD451C" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
9-15 mm lang, 
<normalizedToken id="3BA743CE9F6BBF93C27078561645D8BF" originalValue="1½-2¼" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">11/2-21/4</normalizedToken>
mal so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="630653989AAB5A1C5766CFB09064EBC3" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="3972696E0CD3DE7B2A10EAEDD4745F68" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Samen 1,5-2 mm lang.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="8D4CAFA3F8EF79DEACED46E0155A5951" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer und 
<normalizedToken id="8BFCE5BB62F1BAB7DD5224EF32B921E7" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">frueher</normalizedToken>
Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="588A243F05B531127AD8521CDE63EE81" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">
<emphasis id="37CCDD5628C41BA9C7D1BE35FB3F4854" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="E2D26E9B8F9191F38406DBCAD0FC1196" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">36:</emphasis>
Material aus dem Val Colla (Tessin) (
<normalizedToken id="3B7902C0392BAF96F24A8F9D0130424C" originalValue="Söllner" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Soellner</normalizedToken>
1954).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="724DF3E9CCA1A1EA80ABCC8F63BB56AA" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">
<emphasis id="A82E59DC1B841C951A4CD74D11831106" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin, seltener alpin. Steinige 
<normalizedToken id="3955F170195AA65441349342EDECA1C3" originalValue="Kalkschuttböden" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Kalkschuttboeden</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="2AA814CF03DF637DCD94288FF09D7FAE" originalValue="Geröllhalden" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Geroellhalden</normalizedToken>
, Felsschutt, steinige Rasen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A58E0E7E3D677FDA975EC9004A753BB4" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">
<emphasis id="09A2AB4087CA1DDA5E21585B41C462FC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Verbreitung. Ostalpen-Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="DEF2913EE39BBD44FA8B42634B1C12B2" originalValue="Südostalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Suedostalpen</normalizedToken>
(Val Colla bis Julische Alpen), Nordostalpen (Raxalpe, Eisenerzer Reichenstein, Hochschwab). - Im Gebiet: Val Colla, Bergamasker Alpen (von der Grigna 
<normalizedToken id="DEBC8D0B54A75FE14403D780756A391C" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5BC8B77631F24ED11C3F1EDFB9149FC1" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">
<emphasis id="8ED0114274A34772C1CD2B731B4AC2CB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">
Bemerkungen. 
<taxonomicName id="AE9BF423AEB1031AE1D9A740DFE529D2" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Cerastium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="815" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="austroalpinum">C. austroalpinum</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
steht morphologisch zwischen 
<taxonomicName id="46BD82A9EF328110E0CE76BE35576EC6" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Cerastium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="815" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="latifolium">
<emphasis id="F31B12FDDF91366D787D0C52DFA95FB2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">C. latifolium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
und dem ostalpinen 
<taxonomicName id="81A86A84D22B4BEA19F3421B6880B073" authority="Vest" authorityName="Vest" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Cerastium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="815" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="carinthiacum">
<emphasis id="7EFB82DF50005DB7783156A5439A81B7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">C. carinthiacum</emphasis>
Vest
</taxonomicName>
(durch breit hautrandige 
<normalizedToken id="5DAF7AD3F076C5E1405CF729284D9AD1" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
im 
<normalizedToken id="BBB94812EB7755EA4B2F187C99F39435" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
gekennzeichnet) und soll mit der letzteren auch durch 
<normalizedToken id="C410B8EFE346889282ACBDCE3A4858B0" originalValue="Übergangsformen" pageId="null" pageNumber="815">Uebergangsformen</normalizedToken>
verbunden sein (vgL. Kunz 1950, Kunz und Reichstein 1959).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
